hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Which team do you support? order paxil In an ideal world you would leave this job but I understand that at the moment wage packets aren’t that easy to come by, so it is probably best to stick it out for a while. It won’t be pleasant, but since this happened so quickly hopefully getting over it might be equally speedy. Your boss certainly seems to have moved on without too much dawdling. Take a leaf out of his book and start going on dates. It doesn’t particularly matter with whom, you just need something or someone to distract you from this Mr-and-Mrs fantasy.
